  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf 11 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "11-year-old boy tragically dies after strangulation with rope in Batticaloa",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "A tragic incident in which an 11-year-old boy died after entangling his neck with a rope tied to a house in Bharti Road, Batticaloa Police Division, said that yesterday Friday (22) evening.",
        "An 11-year-old boy named Mathivanan Janusan from Bharati Veethi has died in this way.",
        "In front of the said house, a nylon rope was tied for a scale for placing the goods and the mother was working inside the house at 5 pm on the day of the incident.",
        "The initial investigation of the police revealed that the boy, who was playing alone, was strangled by the rope while playing with his neck tied to it.",
        "After this, the body has been handed over to the Teaching Hospital for post-mortem after obtaining the permission of the court."
      ],
